Subject: Important Information for Q2 Budget Planning

Q2 Profit Forecast is crucial for Q2 budget planning as it helps to ensure that the plan is stick to the profit.
It is important to send the forecast profit for Q2 to help the finance department proceed with the next steps.
If the number provided for Q2 budget confirmation looks off, it may cause delays in the budget planning process.

